=== emerald ===
qty=1 identified buc=blessed -> a blessed emerald
qty=1 identified buc=uncursed -> an uncursed emerald
qty=1 identified buc=cursed -> a cursed emerald
qty=1 identified buc=buc_unknown -> an emerald
qty=1 unidentified -> a green gem
qty=1 called=valuable? -> a gem called valuable?
qty=3 identified buc=blessed -> 3 blessed emeralds
qty=3 identified buc=uncursed -> 3 uncursed emeralds
qty=3 identified buc=cursed -> 3 cursed emeralds
qty=3 identified buc=buc_unknown -> 3 emeralds
qty=3 unidentified -> 3 green gems
qty=3 called=valuable? -> 3 gem called valuable?s
